{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"set"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"incremental"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When incremental sorting is enabled, the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GtkSortListModel"},{"type":"text","text":" will not do"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a complete sort immediately, but will instead queue an idle handler that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"incrementally sorts the items towards their correct position. This of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"course means that items do not instantly appear in the right place. It"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"also means that the total sorting time is a lot slower."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When your filter blocks the UI while sorting, you might consider"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"turning this on. Depending on your model and sorters, this may become"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"interesting around 10,000 to 100,000 items."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, incremental sorting is disabled."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"See [method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gtk.SortListModel.get_pending"},{"type":"text","text":"] for progress information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"about an ongoing incremental sorting operation."}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"varian